Class CatalogDatabaseImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.blazingdb.calcite.catalog.domain.CatalogDatabaseImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.blazingdb.calcite.catalog.domain.CatalogDatabase

    @Entity
public class CatalogDatabaseImpl
extends Object
implements com.blazingdb.calcite.catalog.domain.CatalogDatabase

    Representation of a Database

    This domain class is a database which stores a map of tables that it contains. It is named but currentl we are always defaulting to the same database called "main" as can be seen in ApplicationContext.
    Author:
    felipe
